CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 17, 1955, pg. 20, reads: "Musical Discussion - William G. Nunn Sr., Courier managing editor, and George F. Brown, Courier theatrical expert (far left), join Walt Harper, Pittsburgh bandleader, who just completed a successful week with his crew at Pittsburgh's Midway Lounge, Downtown, and 'Wild Bill' Davis, who recently appeared at the Flamingo Hotel, in a discussion of music on Walt Harper's disc jockey program over WHOD. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: William G. "Bill" Nunn Sr., Walt Harper, "Wild Bill" Davis, and George F. Brown gathered around microphones in WHOD radio station studio
